title: OSINT Research Practicum Project Analyzing Chinese PLA Food Security as Possible Indicator of War in Taiwan
description: Analysis of Food Security Measures Undertaken by the PLA Using Open Source Intelligence Collection Methods, 
Remote Sensing Data, and CNN.
github: https://github.com/JoelElijahManwill/China-OSINT-Practicum-Military-Food-Security-Analysis
